metadata.description:
This first piece of art of my first NFT Series is a component of geography. It speaks to me from a design perspective. I include many topography designs in my graphic designs and in this design, you can find most of the colours I love and all elements of a futuristic design. From typography to unique icons, and illustrations, this first item of the series is all about being original.

The owner of this NFT will receive a Super High-Resolution (8k) version, and a rounded version for social platforms profile pictures.
